**Level 4:** Vibration steers you to specific parallel Earth frame
**Level 5:** Frequency determines which dimensions/beings you can perceive
**Level 6:** Higher frequency = better antenna for higher mind

**Raising Vibration - The Formula:**
1. Act on highest excitement
2. To best ability with no insistence on outcome
